    .custom-app-event__inner
      .custom-app-event__title(v-html='props.acf.event.title')
      .custom-app-event__subtitle(v-html='props.acf.event.subtitle')
      .custom-app-event__content(v-html='props.acf.event.content')
      .custom-app-event__btn(@click='openModal(4)')
        | Register Today
      h3(style="color: white; margin-top: 20px") Please also print this Permission and Release Form and bring with you to the date and time you registered for
      a.custom-app-event__btn(target="_blank" href="https://www.mattiacioortho.com/wp-content/uploads/Mouth-Guard-Permission-and-Release-Form-2022.pdf")
        | Permission and Release Form
